    "Besides, we extract the commonality of each module with reusable templates, and implement vertical templatization design of each module for high-level management.",
    "• We offer a range of eco-services surrounding EduStudio, which can further enable more researchers to understand and quickly participate in the field of student cognitive modeling.",
    "We provide a Github repository that collects valuable resources for student cognitive modeling.",
    "In addition, we develop a Leaderboard website to provide a comprehensive comparison of various models.",
    "BackgroundIn this section, we introduce the category and data description of student cognitive modeling."
